# Sheet Name: Cursor Shortcuts
# App: /Applications/Cursor.app

[General]
⌘I              Toggle Sidepanel
⌘L              Toggle Sidepanel
⌘E              Toggle Agent layout
⌘.              Mode Menu
⌘/              Loop between AI models
⇧⌘J             Cursor settings
⇧⌘Space         Toggle Voice Mode
⌘,              General settings
⇧⌘P             Command palette

[Chat]
⏎               Nudge (default)
⌃⏎              Queue message
⌘⏎              Force send message
⇧⌘⌫             Cancel generation
⇧⌘L             Add selected code as context
⌘V              Add clipboard as context
⇧⌘V             Add clipboard to input box
⌘⌫              Reject all changes
⇥               Cycle to next message
⇧⇥              Rotate between Agent modes
⌥⌘/             Model toggle
⌘N              New chat
⌘R              New chat
⌘T              New chat tab
⌘[              Previous chat
⌘]              Next chat
⌘W              Close chat
esc             Unfocus field

[Inline Edit]
⌘K              Open inline edit
⇧⌘K             Toggle input focus
⏎               Submit
⇧⌘⌫             Cancel
⌥⏎              Ask quick question

[Code Selection & Context]
⇧⌘L             Add selection to Chat
⇧⌘K             Add selection to Edit
⌘L              Add selection to new chat
⌘M              Toggle file reading strategies
⌘→              Accept next word of suggestion
⌘⏎              Search codebase in chat

[Tab]
⇥               Accept suggestion
⌘→              Accept next word

[Terminal]
⌘K              Open terminal prompt bar
⌘⏎              Run generated command
esc             Accept command
